cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with cross-lingual word embeddings and translation. It may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes methods to improve unsupervised learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves natural language processing and language modeling. The use of denoising autoencoder also suggests it could be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper's focus on improving translation could also place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as translation is a common task in image captioning and visual question answering.
